Stone Point Capital LLC, led by
Chairman  Stephen Friedman , joined XL Group Plc in a new venture
to oversee insurance-linked securities.  XL and funds managed by Stone Point will invest as much as
$135 million, the companies said today in a statement
distributed by PR Newswire. XL will have a 75 percent stake in
the company, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
